smw_noboolean: "$1" is not recognised as a Boolean (true/false) value.
smw-admin-settings-docu: Displays a list of all default and localised settings that are relevant to the Semantic MediaWiki environment. For details on individual settings, please consult the [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Configuration configuration] help page.
smw-category-change-propagation-locked-e: The category "$1" has been modified and requires assigned entities to be re-evaluated via a process [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Change_propagation change propagation]. In the meantime, the category page has been locked until the primary specification update is complete to prevent intermediate breaks or conflicting specifications. The process may take a while before the page can be unlocked, as it depends on the size and frequency of the scheduler [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Job_queue job queue].
smw-install-incomplete-populate-hash-fie: The smw_hash field population was skipped during the setup, the [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:populateHashField.php populateHashField.php] script is required to be executed.
